modules.description: Handles string manipulation and indentation removal in test cases. Works with string data types to strip leading whitespace and normalize line breaks. Useful for writing readable multi-line test inputs in source code.

Splits a multi-line string into individual lines and removes leading whitespace uniformly across all lines. Processes strings to align their indentation, making multi-line string constants more readable. Useful when formatting SQL queries, configuration files, or error messages embedded in code.
